{"tid":1251960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"乜而家啲大學咁撚痴線","createTime":"2019-06-22T18:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T18:32:19.000Z","uid":90236,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6bb8a788a77d5182e3d42e88124e537ca61c93","tid":1251960,"uid":90236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟大學有份好重要嘅project要做，grad唔grad到就睇佢<br />\n咁首先就有個freerider組員就話唔鐘意做project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，得閒搵下有咩隱世美食周圍玩打下卡好過啦<br />\n咁我都冇乜所謂，咪自己直接send email問下教授A意見啦<br />\n點知個教授A淨係send番份study plan比我就當解答咗我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲叫我之後去問教授B<br />\n而教授B就叫我問教授C，教授C又叫我問番教授A<br />\n<br />\n咁我就同其他有心做project嘅同學去佢間房直接搵教授A問嘢啦<br />\n我一敲門冇人應，之後就燥燥地大力拍左下門<br />\n教授A就開左門 條煙剷原來係自己房食緊煙，佢話：屌你 做乜衝擊我間房呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後佢仲兜口兜面噴鳩我煙，仲拎左枝棍打咗我一身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同成班同學就嚇撚到跑走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事後我同校方投訴教授A打鳩學生啦<br />\n但校方就話翻查CCTV睇唔到打鳩我果條友係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以追究唔到<br />\n我就問： 屌你點解professor房門口冇名牌架，咁樣點投訴佢呀？<br />\n校方就答我 間房門口都冇位擺名牌 算鳩數啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌你吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學生比教授打 校方都要幫住個撚樣教授<br />\n無耐之後我比教授打嘅消息傳番去個freerider組員，佢就串鳩我話：你收咗隔離間大學幾錢去professor房問野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?抵撚死啦比教授打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，喂大佬份project你都有份架喎<br />\n而家你唔幫手之餘仲要屈鳩我收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你成間大學都痴撚線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f227936588a12a1e719c8ba9d697ffee28af2703","tid":1251960,"uid":118502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:08:32.000Z","msg":"LM 待真心膠出現"},{"pid":"a77a51fab2dfd50a5f57c8cd12ce87a7fc9b26c5","tid":1251960,"uid":24910,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:12:16.000Z","msg":"多左"},{"pid":"ed91e0a14d68c2df87746ee7590887360443a714","tid":1251960,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:19:45.000Z","msg":"好多人都諗住quit U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fa2461c91f71aa82b4b364ede17017418e10cf","tid":1251960,"uid":248925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:27:52.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"10c8d38e7feb528c888398c7a20bb2d9230ea403","tid":1251960,"uid":223816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ecc59d50debdbb2b5844f85bdb90da6ba98613","tid":1251960,"uid":77755,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:32:19.000Z","msg":"知你想曲線 但完全唔明你想up乜 <br />\n唯有最後比返句 兄弟爬山 各有各做 比你"}]}